#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb3.md:167
msgid "Performance Pads"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb3.md:170
msgid ""
"You can use the Pad Mode Select buttons to select a mode for the performance"
" pads. Performance pads are numbered from top left to bottom right. First "
"row is 1-4 and the second row is 5-8. Press shift and the pad mode select "
"button to access other pad modes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb3.md:174
msgid "Hot Cue Mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb3.md:176
msgid ""
"Hot Cue mode is enabled by pressing the {hwlabel}`HOT CUE` button. The "
"button will light up when selected."
msgstr ""

