#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb3.md:195
msgid "Beatjump Mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/pioneer_ddj_sb3.md:197
msgid ""
"Beatjump mode is enabled by holding {hwlabel}`SHIFT` down and pressing the "
"{hwlabel}`HOT CUE` button. The button will flash when selected. Use beatjump"
" mode to jump back or forward on the track by a certain number of beats."
msgstr ""

